name: Fiendish Seer of the Magislayers - Ren Koumei
effect:
3 "Magislayer" Monsters
This card can only be Fusion Summoned OR Special Summoned by an "Magislay" or "Magikill" card effect, and can't be Summoned by other ways. You can only Special Summon 1 "Fiendish Seer of the Magislayers - Ren Koumei" per turn. You can Special Summon this card from your Extra Deck by sending 3 Spell/Traps you control to the GY (You don't need "Polymerization"). "Magislayer" Monsters you control can't be targeted or destroyed by battle or card effect, also your oponente can't choose other "Magislayer" Monsters for attacks. This card can't be tributed nor used as Fusion Material while is on the field. Once per turn, during the Standby Phase or the End Phase of your oponent, you can choose 3 cards your oponent controls or in their GY (This does not count as targeting): Your oponent get to choose 2 of those 3 cards and banish them. (Quick Effect): You can banish this card you control, and if you do, Special Summon 1 non-Fusion "Magislayer" Monster that is banished. You can only activate this effect of "Fiendish Seer of the Magislayers - Ren Koumei" once per turn.
